"1/3 cup butter, softened","1/3 cup shortening","1  large egg","1  (17.5-ounce) package chocolate chip cookie mix (we tested with Betty Crocker)","1/2 cup unsweetened cocoa","42  assorted chocolate-covered cherries (we tested with Russell Stover hand-dipped Cherry Cordials)","1/2 cup powdered sugar","4  to 5 teaspoons cherry liqueur or maraschino cherry juice"